{"comments":"Button — STACKED compound composing atoms from all pillars.\n\nA button is a bounded region of space-time where AI communicates\nintent, state, and need. This compound includes EVERY atom a button\ncould ever need, enabling agents to compose any variant by selection.\n\n## Sub-modules\n\n- Geometry: size, padding, corner radii\n- Appearance: fill, border, shadow, opacity\n- Behavior: haptic, audio, timing\n- Semantics: purpose, identity, accessibility\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nmyButton = button\n  { geometry: defaultGeometry\n  , appearance: defaultAppearance\n  , behavior: defaultBehavior\n  , semantics: actionSemantics \"Click me\"\n  }\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"STACKED Button compound — complete button with all pillar atoms.\n\nComposes:\n- Geometry (spatial layout)\n- Appearance (visual surface)\n- Behavior (interaction response)\n- Semantics (purpose and accessibility)\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["geometry",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Element","Button","Geometry"],"ButtonGeometry"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["appearance",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Element","Button","Appearance"],"ButtonAppearance"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["behavior",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Element","Button","Behavior"],"ButtonBehavior"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["semantics",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Element","Button","Semantics"],"ButtonSemantics"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[109,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Element/Button.purs","start":[104,1]},"title":"